jiang cotton.<br />\n<br />\nCompanies highlighted by social media users so far include Zara owner Inditex; PVH - owner of Calvin Klein and Tommy Hilfiger; VF Corp - which owns The North Face; and Abercrombie &amp; Fitch.<br />\n<br />\nInditex is accused of removing a statement from its website stating the company&rsquo;s &quot;zero-tolerance&quot; approach to forced labour and that it did not have relationships with any factories in Xinjiang. PVH and Abercrombie &amp; Fitch are also accused of removing statements on Xinjiang. VF Corp removed a statement but later reinstated it.<br />\n<br />\nAnother fashion brand, Hugo Boss, reportedly told its Chinese customers that it would continue to &ldquo;purchase and support&rdquo; Xinjiang cotton even though a statement on its website says it has not directly sourced from the region."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T05:51:05.000Z","msg":"Nike無得唔企硬喇<br />\n基本上成單嘢最早係因Nike而起"},{"pid":"8dfa687e7a678bf502197aeb74224106e19a3c7a","tid":2480930,"uid":56956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"40d49ee5f16b1a31fd8893c89cc6644f69988bb2","tid":2480930,"uid":292987,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T02:40:14.000Z","msg":"點解日企咁興啲廢老藍絲tone 以為咁講好穩陣好保險 吃屎啦種族滅絕面前保持中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T05:54:22.000Z","msg":"事實係最保險 <br />\n唔係香港 白羅斯 呢類地方 <br />\n大多數人都唔太留意呢類新聞"},{"pid":"f6a60c894704fa9730c5f7c6eb2b5f235629fbcb","tid":2480930,"uid":120400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T05:59:09.000Z","msg":"買u記唔可以上連登講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebc6030372e90f4c8c515088e63d6aee7d2c697","tid":2480930,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6befa98bffe3501a2d43dd127b8610074b0e0ab6","tid":2480930,"uid":33939,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T02:13:20.000Z","msg":"好簡單，唔需要comment。有冇用同會唔會繼續用先係問題。"},"cite